channel.title: Virus
channel.description:
Well, i dled a source and ran it, and got a virus and now any cm type thing i go to says "The command prompt has been disabled by your administrator" Press any key to continue...
Help please..:S

item.title: Virus
item.dc:creator: @Ksu Ksu
item.description:
@Ksu wrote:

Click start, run, and enter this:

REG add HKCU\Software\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\System /v DisableCMD /t REG_DWORD /d 0 /f
